            . I am a <rs id="t18300527-149-viclabel812" type="occupation">tailor and slop-seller</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-149-victim1258 t18300527-149-viclabel812"></join>. The prisoner came to me last Saturday, and brought this note from another ship; he wanted clothes to the amount of 20s., and one sovereign which I gave him for the amount of the note - he said he was going to the ship in a great hurry.</p>
               <p>This was a note similar to the last, but stating him to belong to the ship Alice, and drawn for 2l.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300527-149-person1260">
                  JOSEPH 
                  ENEVER
               <interp inst="t18300527-149-person1260" type="surname" value="ENEVER"></interp>
